name: BABI GULING PAK DODOT
address: Sumberkima, Gerokgak, Buleleng Regency, Bali 81155, Indonesia
review 1: Went twice during my stay. Great Babi Guling, friendly and efficient service. Normal price. Broth soup had great flavour
review 2: We had lunch here after snorkeling tour. This is my first try of Babi Guling and fall love into this. Sate babi, crispy skin and other meats were so good. I also like their orange juice which comes with lime in it :-).
review 3: Really good Babi guling. Great flavours. Staff will make less spicy for children. Added element of sate babi, pork rib and hot tasty soup to flavour your rice. Refreshing ice tea too.
review 4: Delicious taste of babi guling üòç spices are on point. Pork is delicious. The staff is friendly. Nice food near the sumberkima/menjangan area in Bali.
review 5: Love the satay and soup that comes with the Baby Guling menu. It is very juicy and flavorful.

name: Umma Bali Menjangan
address: Gang Taman Tukad Salak, Sumberkima, Kec. Gerokgak, Kabupaten Buleleng, Bali 81155, Indonesia
review 1:
Very cozy place. It's a great place for couples. Super nice plunge pool and the beds were among the best beds I've come across.
I wish there were more charging points though. Nevertheless. It's a really good place to spend a night or two
review 2: We had an amazing stay! Lovely little joglo bungalows in the middle of ricefields. Such a great host. Thanks, we will come back!
review 3: Had an amazing time at this place! The area is just beautiful, the bed was like a dream, and the breakfast was delicious. Plus, the host went above and beyond ‚Äì super friendly and helpful!
review 4:
Lovely place ‚ù§

The owner is very kind and escorts us to the room by himself, everything is very well prepared, nice view, very very clean, and the room smells really nice.

I wish I could stay longer here.
review 5: This place is absolutely amazing it‚Äôs run by a family and Made (the owner)will look after your every needs. The cottages are absolutely charming comfortable and to die for. It has a swimming pool and they do breakfast, dinner and tea, not far from the water snorkelling and many other activities, one of the best spots of ever stayed in Bali.

name: Gara Menjangan Homestay
address: Sumberkima, Gerokgak, Buleleng Regency, Bali 81155, Indonesia
review 1: Had a lovely stay here for 2 nights. The room is clean and comfortable and the location is quiet and with a lovely garden. The staff were super friendly and made us feel so welcome. 100% recommend staying at Gara Menjangan :)
review 2: We had 2 wonderful nights there. The garden is clean and well maintained. Breakfasts were excellent with rice, eggs, fruit and fresh juice. Felt like home there.
review 3: Lovely stay here for three nights in August. Owner and his family were so lovely and the room was spacious and clean.
review 4:
I really recommend this place for anyone who seeks a peaceful place with authentic balinese village vibe.
They offer a really pleasing experience and hospitality, serve you welcome drink, and also breakfast. The owner would willingly take us to the beach near the place if we want to.
review 5:
Great homestay with amazing rooms for the price and a beautiful garden.
The host is extremely accommodating and cooks great food, he made me baba gueling for lunch üëå

name: JFC Fried Chicken at Sumberkima
address: VJ44+R2G, Jl. Singaraja-Gilimanuk, Sumberkima, Kec. Gerokgak, Kabupaten Buleleng, Bali 81155, Indonesia
review 1:
This fried-chicken restaurant is like an oasis in the middle of our exploration of the dry-humid north-west side of Bali. Thank you for being there. The food is good. The staff are polite and responsive.

Some of the noticeable differences of this JFC with other JFCs in Bali:
- The tables are clean and glossy, the chairs are comfortable (brand Informa)
- There are 2 rooms of WC. Clean and smell good. Also the first time to see Trilliunware brand firsthand
review 2: very clean place & very friendly service...

name: MI AYAM BAKSO "CAK RUDI"
address: Jl. Seririt-Gilimanuk, Sumberkima, Kec. Gerokgak, Kabupaten Buleleng, Bali 81155, Indonesia
review 1: Very good food similar to chicken stock with noodles soup, wit addition of veggies and meatballs. It's an authentic place with very friendly service. The prices are very affordable.
